headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co.'s Transformative Move Adds Value
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. announced the acquisition of AssuredPartners, which will be a transformative acquisition at a gross cost of $13.45 billion. Read more here.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher buys Sheila J. Butler & Company
summary: The SJB team will continue operating from its current site under the leadership of Gallagher Southeast employee benefits head Colby Paxton.
